<div class="card">
  <div class="card-header">
    <h2>The GatherPack Story</h2>
  </div>
  <div class="card-body">
    <p>
      GatherPack's journey began with <a href="https://boilerinvasion.org" target="_blank">a FIRST Robotics Competition team</a> drowning in spreadsheets and sticky notes.
      In those days, critical information about meeting attendance, fundraising progress, and team logistics was scattered across multiple files, desks, and brains.
      This fragmented system made it challenging for mentors, team members, and parents to keep track of everything they needed to know without going around and asking people.
    </p>

    <p>
      <a href="https://brad-thompson.com" target="_blank">One of the volunteers with the program</a>, a web developer by trade, decided to fix this with a simple little web application.
      This brought all of that operational information together in one place that everyone on the team could access.
    </p>

    <p>
      And now, almost 10 years later, <a href="https://westside-robotics.info" target="_blank">the organization behind that team</a> has basically quadrupled in size &amp; scope - 
      and that original tool has started to show its age and inability to keep up with some of the ways that the organization runs now.
      That same volunteer and a few of the students on the team decided to build a new tool from the ground up,
      built to be more flexible, capable, and robust to handle not only their needs, 
      but the needs of other teams and organizations that have been looking for a tool like this to help keep their groups more organized.
      And we're partnering with said volunteer's <a href="https://sledgehammerinfosystems.com" target="_blank">software &amp; consulting company</a> to provide hosting, implementation, and custom development services too!
    </p>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="card">
  <div class="card-header">
    <h2>Tools &amp; Features</h2>
  </div>
  <div class="card-body">
    <div class="row align-items-center">
      <div class="col-4 col-md-2">
        <i class="fa-5x fa-solid fa-person"></i>
      </div>
      <div class="col-8 col-md-4">
        <h3>People</h3>
        Keep track of everyone associated with your organization in one place, whether they have an account in the system or not.
      </div>
      <div class="col-12 col-md-6">
        <div class="row align-items-center my-3">
          <div class="col-8 col-md-6 col-xl-9">
            <h4>Teams</h4>
            Group people together into different teams to manage their access to information and segment communication.
          </div>
          <div class="col-4 col-md-6 col-xl-3">
            <i class="fa-4x fa-duotone fa-solid fa-users"></i>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="row align-items-center my-3">
          <div class="col-8 col-md-6 col-xl-9">
            <h4>Managers</h4>
            Grant certain users the ability to manage content, events, and people on their teams.
          </div>
          <div class="col-4 col-md-6 col-xl-3">
            <i class="fa-4x fa-duotone fa-solid fa-user-tie"></i>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="row align-items-center my-3">
          <div class="col-8 col-md-6 col-xl-9">
            <h4>Badges</h4>
            Assign badges to people to track their achievements - or just for fun!
          </div>
          <div class="col-4 col-md-6 col-xl-3">
            <i class="fa-4x fa-duotone fa-solid fa-certificate"></i>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <hr>

    <div class="row align-items-center">
      <div class="col-4 col-md-2">
        
        <i class="fa-5x fa-solid fa-message"></i>
      </div>
      <div class="col-8 col-md-4">
        <h3>Announcements</h3>
        Post team-specific or site-wide announcements that can be scheduled to appear &amp; disappear as needed.
        
      </div>
      <div class="col-12 col-md-6">
        <div class="row align-items-center my-3">
          <div class="col-8 col-md-6 col-xl-9">
            <h4>Messaging</h4>
            Manage inbound &amp; outbound communications via email, text, Slack, Discord, and more!*
          </div>
          <div class="col-4 col-md-6 col-xl-3">
            <i class="fa-4x fa-duotone fa-solid fa-comments"></i>
