      <div class="col-4 col-md-2">
        <i class="fa-5x fa-solid fa-money-bill"></i>
      </div>
      <div class="col-8 col-md-4">
        <h3>Finance Tools</h3>
        Simplify your life by tracking your organization's finances in the same place as the rest of your important information.
      </div>
      <div class="col-12 col-md-6">
        <div class="row align-items-center my-3">
          <div class="col-8 col-md-6 col-xl-9">
            <h4>Bookeeping</h4>
            Keep your finances organized with our flexible transaction tagging system.
          </div>
          <div class="col-4 col-md-6 col-xl-3">
            <i class="fa-4x fa-duotone fa-solid fa-file-invoice-dollar"></i>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="row align-items-center my-3">
          <div class="col-8 col-md-6 col-xl-9">
            <h4>Payment Processing</h4>
            Directly collect &amp; track payments or donations through GatherPack. *
          </div>
          <div class="col-4 col-md-6 col-xl-3">
            <i class="fa-4x fa-duotone fa-solid fa-hand-holding-dollar"></i>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <hr>

    <div class="row align-items-center">
      <div class="col-4 col-md-2">
        <i class="fa-5x fa-solid fa-calendar"></i>
      </div>
      <div class="col-8 col-md-4">
        <h3>Events</h3>
        Get an at-a-glance view of all of the important happenings within your organization, either directly in GatherPack or through your Google Calendar or other calendaring tools.
      </div>
      <div class="col-12 col-md-6">
        <div class="row align-items-center my-3">
          <div class="col-8 col-md-6 col-xl-9">
            <h4>Check-In</h4>
            Let people RSVP to events - and keep track of custom information like volunteer roles or hotel room assignments.
          </div>
          <div class="col-4 col-md-6 col-xl-3 my-3">
            <i class="fa-4x fa-duotone fa-solid fa-calendar-check"></i>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="row align-items-center my-3">
          <div class="col-8 col-md-6 col-xl-9">
            <h4>Time Tracking</h4>
            Keep track of people's attendance as they volunteer or work for your organization, either via manual entry or our time clock kiosk.
          </div>
          <div class="col-4 col-md-6 col-xl-3">
            <i class="fa-4x fa-duotone fa-solid fa-user-clock"></i>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <hr>

    <div class="row align-items-center">
      <div class="col-4 col-md-2">
        <i class="fa-5x fa-solid fa-laptop-code"></i>
      </div>
      <div class="col-8 col-md-4">
        <h3>Automation</h3>
        Power users can write custom code snippets to automate tasks of all sorts throughout the system.
      </div>
      <div class="col-12 col-md-6">
        <div class="row align-items-center my-3">
          <div class="col-8 col-md-6 col-xl-9">
            <h4>Reports</h4>
            Get custom-built insights into your organization's data.
          </div>
          <div class="col-4 col-md-6 col-xl-3">
            <i class="fa-4x fa-duotone fa-solid fa-file-code"></i>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="row align-items-center my-3">
          <div class="col-8 col-md-6 col-xl-9">
            <h4>Actions</h4>
            Allow your users to trigger custom tasks throughout GatherPack.*
          </div>
          <div class="col-4 col-md-6 col-xl-3">
            <i class="fa-4x fa-duotone fa-solid fa-wand-sparkles"></i>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="row align-items-center my-3">
          <div class="col-8 col-md-6 col-xl-9">
            <h4>Hooks</h4>
            Run custom actions in response to anything that happens in the system.
          </div>
          <div class="col-4 col-md-6 col-xl-3">
            <i class="fa-4x fa-duotone fa-solid fa-code-pull-request"></i>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <p class="small text-center mt-2 mx-5">
      * Some of these features are still in development and will be available soon!
    </p>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="card">
  <div class="card-header">
    <h2>Built by the Community, for the Community</h2>
  </div>
  <div class="card-body">
    <p>
      GatherPack stands out in the crowded field of organization management software because it's being built by people 
      who are using it on a daily basis to run real organizations.
      There are other similar-ish tools out there, but they tend to be either incredibly expensive, unnecessarily complicated, 
      or built more around the idea of a passive group - like a membership-driven non-profit that hosts a fundraiser dinner twice a year - 
      than a very active, multi-layered, excited mass of people.
    </p>

    <p>
      The core GatherPack platform is free &amp; open source so anybody with a little technical know-how can run this for their organization.
      We are also offering affordable hosting, support, and custom development services through our founder's company, 
      <a href="https://sledgehammerinfosystems.com" target="_blank">Sledgehammer Infosystems</a>
    </p>
  </div>
</div>

